author: stsp
msg: (TestHarness): In the progress callbacks, exit early if the expected number
of dots have already been printed.

author: suresh
msg: HADOOP-8457. Address file ownership issue for users in Admin group on windows. Contributed by Ivan Mitc.

author: stsp
msg: (TestHarness): In the progress callbacks, if we're not logging to a file,
we won't be printing anything. So simply exit early instead of performing
computations we're not going to use for anything. Also, for purely cosmetic
reasons, trim empty lines from the progress callbacks.
